Site Comment: The blackwall reach site changed location from original coordinates e385081; n6456807 to those detailed in this form from 13/12/2010. The original site was a private mooring which swan river trust had an agreement to use.This mooring broke and was temporarily unavailable and it was then decided to permanently move the site location approximately 230m upstream to the swan river trust owned mooring. The new location is in a similar depth of water (15-16m) and is considered to be the same site with respect to data collection and analysis.
